The paper discusses the use of directional modulation for secure transmission in various communication channels such as millimeter wave (mmWave) massive MIMO, satellite communication, UAV, and smart transportation. This indicates that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Multimedia (cs.MM), and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. However, since the paper primarily focuses on the secure transmission aspect, it is most likely to belong to the Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) sub-category.
